UID:K3HY3oyLJ6KyOZ0YokcBu
SUMMARY:French classical music
DTSTAMP:20260314T153802Z
DTSTART:20260320T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:University District (4.6 miles NE)\n\nAugustin Hadelich & Franc
	esco Piemontesi are a noted German violinist and a Swiss pianist playing m
	usic by French composers Rameau\, Poulenc\, Franck\, and Debussy\, plus th
	e Hungarian Kurtág at Meany Center for the Performing Arts\, 4040 George W
	ashington Lane NE in Seattle.\n\nhttps://meanycenter.org/tickets/2026-03/p
	roduction/augustin-hadelich-violin-francesco-piemontesi-piano?ref=encorepl
	us.app\n\nFrom Events12 Seattle
URL:https://meanycenter.org/tickets/2026-03/production/augustin-hadelich-vi
