SUMMARY:Brain festival
DTSTAMP:20260314T153803Z
DTSTART:20260321T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle Center (1 mile NW)\n\nBrainFest includes shows\, talks\
	, and exhibitions about the human brain at Pacific Science Center\, 200 2n
